  <brief_title>Anxiety and Depression in Patients Hospitalizes for an Acute Exacerbation of COPD</brief_title>
  <acronym>ADPHA-EPOC</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Trial to Asses the Efficacy of an Early Psychiatric Counseling Compared to Usual Care in a Cohort of Patients Hospitalized for an Acute Exacerbation of COPD in Prevention of Re-exacerbation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
