  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will try to elucidate wheter the impact of a psychiatric intervention in patients
      hospitalized because an acute exacerbation of COPD and anxiety/depression and reconsulting at
      1 and 6 month after discharge.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
